# Salesforce CRM Application

## Overview
This project is a custom CRM built on Salesforce to manage customers and leads.

## Features
- Custom Objects (My Customer, My Lead)
- Lookup Relationship (Lead → Customer)
- Automation using Flow
- Apex Trigger for Lead Qualification
- Reports and Dashboard

## Tech Stack
- Salesforce CRM
- Apex
- Flow Builder
- Lightning Experience

## Functionality
- Lead is automatically marked as "Qualified" when linked to a customer
